Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主線任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…小結衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結衣 我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼能從這裡扔出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嘗試用警告模式呼叫過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡片?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺 你知道這是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒見過這種道具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有彈出窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是用於系統管理的訪問代碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說只要有了這個就能行使GM權限了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遊戲內部連接系統需要相應的控制台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也無法呼叫出系統菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西不可能無緣無故就掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是媽媽察覺到我們在這裡之後扔下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺 你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往世界樹的門在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在樹根部的穹頂裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有守護者駐守著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今為止無論是多強的大軍都無法突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我也得去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我會一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道通往那穹頂的路線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上前方的臺階後 馬上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒關係嗎 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據至今為止的情報來推測
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要突破大門是十分困難的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失敗了也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再磨蹭哪怕一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會瘋掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣也想快點見到媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不識天高地厚者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝欲往王城乎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}是否挑戰主線任務「世界樹的守護者」?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然則示以汝背雙翼之足可翱翔哉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就向我等證明你背上的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把頭藏好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜 亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差…還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差…一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}復活剩餘時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 我打從心裡覺得這個世界只是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是報應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的強大說穿了也不過是技能數值和個人參數而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為自己能超越遊戲的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越極限 無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有死亡壓力的遊戲實在太輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 莉琺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要再這麼亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 你一個人是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回平時的桐人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉琺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去那裡的話就什麼都無法了結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都無法開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須再去見她一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見亞絲娜一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我在找的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直葉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小直
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}確定要登出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直 我可進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一個人呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小直
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也很驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為我還在使用NERvGear一事生氣的話 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無論如何都需要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…背叛了自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了喜歡哥哥的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺忘一切 放棄一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要喜歡上桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是已經喜歡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道 我們可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和哥哥不是親兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前我就已經知道這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥之所以要放棄劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以要避開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你一早就知道這個事實了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不是親妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直在疏遠我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今為什麼還要對我這麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對於哥哥能夠從SAO裡面回來真的感到很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠像小時候那樣和我融洽相處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為哥哥你終於能接受我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如繼續對我不理不睬好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用察覺到自己對哥哥的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用因知道亞絲娜的事而感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用喜歡上代替哥哥的桐人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直

Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:22.54,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高く高く この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:26.60,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと きっと って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:32.42,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう一度願うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.07,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とめどない想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.58,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}日常に飲まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.96,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}揺らめきながらまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.69,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}形を変えていった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.39,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今さらもう遅いかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.84,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}返事のない自問自答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.22,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}すべてはそう自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:12.53,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}終わりも始まりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:19.74,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}高く高く この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:26.91,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}優しい光を目指して羽ばたくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:34.16,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心に灯した情熱を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.30,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと きっと って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.50,ED2JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう一度願うから

Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:22.54,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}更高更高向著那蒼穹伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:26.60,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會默念著承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:32.42,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再度祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:47.07,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永無止息的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.58,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}被日常所湮沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.96,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在搖曳中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:57.69,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再次改變了姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:01.39,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}事到如今是否已太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.84,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我向著虛空自問自答道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.22,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}其實一切都取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:12.53,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論終結還是開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:19.74,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}更高更高向著那蒼穹伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:26.91,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}朝著那溫和的光芒展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:34.16,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也不忘擁緊那燃點於心中的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.30,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會默念著承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:42.50,ED2CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再度祈願

